President Uhuru’s Big Four agenda are increasingly becoming a tall order to realise especially with his tenure approaching its end. Kenyans have a thousand small things that need fixing before they can internalise what Big Four agenda means. Why talk of big things when small things are yelling for attention; bothering with a log when we cannot remove the little speck in our eyes? Let’s break down the agenda into bite-size goals because we are racing against time for the remaining tenure. Otherwise, they will remain a dream.  MA student of Project Planning and Management at UoN